Fixed bug where zones can't be deleted

Each deleted record will trigger a signal handler which increment zone serial.
This is a problem when a zone itself is deleted and all its records are removed,
this change will ignore DoesNotExist error when trying to increment zone
serial while record deletion.

commit_list.message:
Added field alternative in patterns

It is now possible to define, in view pattern, alternates fields to get,
if the previous field can't be found in the movies attributes.

For example, the following pattern will take the french title if defined,
or the original one.

    "{title_fr|original_title}"
